						<div class="postbody">I am currently working on a Final Fantasy project, and I was wondering about Final Fantasy's maps. Are they based on 2x2 meta tiles? Do they have different sizes? I'm really really concerned that I may not have enough space for maps, and I'm wondering how the other Final Fantasies work. Does anybody know how they conserve space? Like Final Fantasy 3 for instance? Any multiple size metatiles?</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.freewebs.com/the_bott/" class="postlink">-Owner of Poultry Games</a></div>
